Package: ALprekDB
Type: Package
Title: Alabama Pre-K Administrative Data Processing and Database Management
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: person("JoonHo", "Lee",
                  email = "jlee296@ua.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-4019-8703"))
Description: A modular toolkit for processing, cleaning, validating, and
    managing Alabama First Class Pre-K (FCPK) administrative records. This
    package standardizes annual data processing workflows for budget, classroom,
    and student data files received from ADECE (Alabama Department of Early
    Childhood Education). Features include: data-driven column mapping via
    external codebooks, pattern-based format detection across file versions,
    reconciliation diagnostics, derived variable creation, multi-year panel
    construction, cross-module linkage with join diagnostics, classroom-level
    student aggregation, DuckDB-based persistent storage with SQL query
    support, and multiple export formats.
